botConfig.name: system.errorExpiredSessionPrompt
botConfig.description: The message when the session has expired
botConfig.value: Your session has expired.  Please start again.

botConfig.name: system.errorUnexpectedErrorPrompt
botConfig.description: The message when there is an unexpected error
botConfig.value: Oops I'm encountering a spot of trouble. Please try again later...

botConfig.name: system.intentConfidenceThreshold
botConfig.description: The minimum confidence score required to match a skill's intent with user input. If there is no match, the transition action is set to 'unresolvedIntent'.(Minimum value 0, maximum value 1)

botConfig.name: system.oauthCancelPrompt
botConfig.description: The message when OAuth authorization is canceled

botConfig.name: system.errorMaxStatesExceededPrompt
botConfig.description: The message when the Bot appears to be an infinite loop
botConfig.value: Your session appears to be in an infinite loop.

botConfig.name: system.oauthSuccessPrompt
botConfig.description: The message when OAuth authorization succeeds
botConfig.value: Authentication successful! You can return to the conversation.

botConfig.name: system.intentConfidenceWinMargin
botConfig.description: Only the top intent that exceeds the confidence threshold is picked if its confidence score exceeds that of other intents by this value or more. If other intents that exceed the confidence threshold have scores that are within that of the top intent by less than the win margin, these intents are also presented to the user. (Minimum value 0, maximum value 1)
